cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with generating images of objects with specific geometric attributes, specifically faces. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The method also involves using a statistical shape model and enforcing geometry through a differentiable geometric transformation, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper presents experimental results on face generation, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
